data.description: Beautiful, one-of-a-kind home located in the highly sought after 28409 area.   This home has been meticulously maintained with every detail attended to.  Featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and 2 half bathrooms, you'll find fresh paint, new toilets, and plantation blinds throughout.  The home is located on a quiet cul-de-sac and boasts a built-in security system for added peace of mind.  A 22KW whole house generator is included.  Other highlights of this home include new windows, stainless steel appliances, low maintenance LVP flooring, gas logs, and 2 brand new mini-split heating and air units that were recently installed.  There is ample parking available for anything from an RV to a boat or multiple vehicles.  Abundant outdoor storage is also available via two large storage buildings.  This 3100+ square foot property is located just 5 minutes from shopping and restaurants and a mere 5 miles from the beach
